1
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,239
The exhibition is well arranged.

2
00:01:15,599 --> 00:01:17,000
Let's go and see other places.

3
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,079
OK.

4
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:22,519
Are you sick?

5
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,319
I stayed up late last night.

6
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:27,040
I'm afraid of delaying the work.

7
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,760
Your health is the most important.

8
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,560
Don't work so hard.

9
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:31,760
I'll find someone to replace you.

10
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,359
Go back and take care of yourself.

11
00:01:34,359 --> 00:01:35,120
Go.

12
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:37,359
Boss Ke.

13
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,639
Old classmate,

14
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,960
sorry to keep you waiting.

15
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,879
Let me take you to the exhibition.

16
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,919
You said you didn't have time to catch up with me before.

17
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,240
Did you come to Harbor City

18
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,080
to give me a surprise?

19
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,319
Did Shen Shutu mention

20
00:02:42,199 --> 00:02:43,199
his visit to Harbor City?

21
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:46,639
We haven't been in touch

22
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,439
since we broke up.

23
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,159
I'm here in Harbor City

24
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,560
to discuss a partnership

25
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,159
with the Shan Yuan Charity Fund.

26
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,960
We're old classmates.

27
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,039
You know what to do.

28
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,319
I'll make sure to show you a good time.

29
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,560
But,

30
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,919
Harbor City's got great horse racing.

31
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:08,680
Isn't that more fun than an art show?

32
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:12,439
Are you interested in the art exhibition

33
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:14,560
or the people here?

34
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:17,080
She and I

35
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,000
are history.

36
00:03:24,319 --> 00:03:25,439
Shutup, look.

37
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,159
This pair of lovebirds

38
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:28,479
are free and easy,

39
00:03:28,759 --> 00:03:30,639
with a rapport that others can't match.

40
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,319
Unlike some people,

41
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,639
who seem like a couple,

42
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:36,199
but one of them has long been distracted.

43
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:37,840
You're wrong.

44
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,719
Nowadays, many people look at paintings

45
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,719
only at the price and fame,

46
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:46,759
they don't understand paintings at all.

47
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,759
Just like some people fall in love

48
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:50,560
only for a moment of novelty,

49
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,479
but forget that mandarin ducks

50
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,639
are all about being faithful to one another.

51
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,879
Miss Jiang is good at restoring cultural relics,

52
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,840
but not necessarily good at dating.

53
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,159
That's true.

54
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:06,199
That's why my ex

55
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,319
ignored me.

56
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:09,439
I have to catch him myself.

57
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,719
Can we talk?

58
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,080
Ex?

59
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,560
Shutu has official business with me.

60
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,519
Your private matters

61
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,279
can wait.

62
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:19,879
Official business?

63
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,279
Shen Shutu,

64
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,680
there's nothing

65
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,519
between us.

66
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:31,560
Let's go.

67
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,680
Miss Jiang is sick.

68
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,879
Take care of her.

69
00:04:52,839 --> 00:04:53,800
Xunxun,

70
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,040
how are you?

71
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,000
I'll be fine after eating some porridge.

72
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,240
Senior fellow student,

73
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,160
do you know the relationship

74
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,480
between him and Miss Lin?

75
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,519
They were classmates in high school.

76
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,720
I don't know much about it.

77
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,720
But it's not surprising for a guy like Shen Shutu

78
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:12,000
to have

79
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,319
a lot of girlfriends.

80
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:16,800
Here.

81
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:31,800
Xunxun,

82
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,680
sometimes, love

83
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,000
doesn't have to hit the wall

84
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,360
to turn back.

85
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,000
As long as you're willing,

86
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,160
I'll always be there for you.

87
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,399
I know you mean it,

88
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,399
but over the years,

89
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:51,160
I've only seen you as a senior fellow student.

90
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,439
It's okay.

91
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:55,480
I can wait.

92
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,759
Have some porridge.

93
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:09,959
After eating, get some sleep.

94
00:06:28,399 --> 00:06:29,920
Miss Jiang is seriously ill,

95
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,720
but she's right about one thing.

96
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,079
I should be more straightforward.

97
00:06:34,319 --> 00:06:35,120
Shutu,

98
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,360
the happiest days

99
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,800
I can think of from childhood to adulthood

100
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,800
are when I sat at the same desk with you.

101
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,720
I have cherished this photo all along.

102
00:06:52,759 --> 00:06:53,600
Now I give it to you.

103
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,759
I narrowly beat you by one place in that mock exam.

104
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,399
It's also the only time in my life

105
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:03,160
that I've ever beaten you.

106
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,240
I remember.

107
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,120
I remember we made a plan

108
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,360
to go to a concert together

109
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,600
after graduation.

110
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,759
But you stood me up.

111
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,160
I'm sorry.

112
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,600
I had already decided to go abroad

113
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,600
and left without saying goodbye.

114
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:21,240
I've been regretting it ever since.

115
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,399
I shouldn't have kept it from you.

116
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:24,120
Shutong,

117
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,000
can you forgive me?

118
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,279
Miss Lin,

119
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,680
I thought you came to me today

120
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:36,600
to talk about the fund cooperation.

121
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,920
There's no hurry.

122
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:44,560
What's this medicine for?

123
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,279
A guy like you

124
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,240
also has trouble sleeping?

125
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,120
Actually, I'm curious.

126
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:57,360
Didn't you used to regard researching high-tech programs

127
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,600
as your dream?

128
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:00,600
Why did you inherit the family business?

129
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,360
It's just a show.

130
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:05,000
The board members

131
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:05,959
are annoying.

132
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:07,360
They make me stressed.

133
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,920
Besides,

134
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,399
my father is getting old.

135
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,360
He wants me to go back to the group.

136
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,720
What about you?

137
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,600
How's your study abroad?

138
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:19,319
It's late.

139
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,759
I won't disturb your rest.

140
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,519
We can talk

141
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:24,000
another time.

142
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,959
Sleeping pills are bad for your health.

143
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:29,319
Take care.

144
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,519
Okay.

145
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:36,759
Shutong,

146
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,960
you can take some time off in Harbor City.

147
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,600
Consider it a break for yourself.

148
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,559
That's what I'm thinking.

149
00:08:45,559 --> 00:08:46,799
Then get some rest.

150
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:47,919
I'll come to see you tomorrow.

151
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:48,600
Okay.

152
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,840
What about this photo?

153
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:02,360
Put it there.

154
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,519
Master.

155
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:30,799
When we catch Ke Yu'ang,

156
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,279
remember to give me a long vacation.

157
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:33,720
Okay.

158
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:35,080
I'll approve your vacation.

159
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:37,759
Okay.

160
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,440
You little rascal,

161
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,840
are you badmouthing me to Wei Chuan again?

162
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:07,000
You and Wei Chuan are both soldiers I trained.

163
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,240
I know

164
00:10:08,919 --> 00:10:10,919
you and him are not just master and apprentice,

165
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,919
but also comrades-in-arms who fought side by side.

166
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:15,480
He's gone,

167
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,440
and it leaves a hole in my heart.

168
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:19,360
Wei Chuan's sacrifice

169
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:20,679
is all my fault.

170
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,799
If I had gone with him,

171
00:10:25,919 --> 00:10:27,200
he wouldn't have died.

172
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:30,440
Different paths.

173
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,480
Indeed, different paths.

174
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,320
Everyone

175
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:38,440
walks a different path in life,

176
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:39,879
but the destination

177
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:41,440
is the same.

178
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:43,919
We walk the path of guardianship.

179
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:45,639
Even if we

180
00:10:45,639 --> 00:10:47,080
lose our lives on this path,

181
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,600
it's also

182
00:10:48,919 --> 00:10:49,879
the same destination.

183
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,240
Come on.

184
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:58,919
To Wei Chuan.

185
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:14,159
I wanted

186
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,360
to wait until you were feeling better

187
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,200
before sending you back.

188
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:19,440
But now there's a new situation.

189
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,159
We thought

190
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:22,679
after the spy got Jiaotu No.1,

191
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:24,240
he would start production immediately.

192
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,679
But now it seems

193
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,000
they haven't made any moves.

194
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:30,240
According to our intelligence,

195
00:11:30,759 --> 00:11:31,600
Ke Yu'ang

196
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,120
hasn't made any moves yet.

197
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,080
Captain Feng,

198
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:36,039
I request

199
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:38,559
to go to Harbor City to investigate.

200
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:13,120
[The photo frame given by Lin Chuyi to Shen Shutu]

201
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:15,720
[is not only a carrier of unforgettable memories,]

202
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:18,720
[but also a pair of eyes watching him.]

203
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:21,360
Article 15 of the Counter-Espionage Law

204
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:22,840
of the People's Republic of China

205
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,360
stipulates that no individual or organization

206
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,919
shall illegally produce,

207
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:26,360
sell, possess, or use

208
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,679
specialized espionage equipment

209
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:29,679
that is specifically required

210
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:31,240
for espionage activities.

211
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,480
In daily life,

212
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,200
if you discover

213
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,720
equipment with functions

214
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,720
such as secret photography, recording,

215
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,080
eavesdropping, positioning,

216
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,639
and secret transmission,

217
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:39,919
you must immediately

218
00:12:39,919 --> 00:12:41,679
call 12339

219
00:12:41,679 --> 00:12:43,960
to report to the national security agency.
